{"tid":1430492,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大家請開始進入運動另一階段","createTime":"2019-08-07T18:05:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T00:56:26.000Z","uid":287028,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c25c0d2f37ed27bd07dea0b5f3f12de27ca2731c","tid":1430492,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T18:05:21.000Z","msg":"大家最近好似完全比政府spin走晒 focus, 不如黎一招萬佛朝宗，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">擒賊先擒王</span></span>。 <br />\n<br />\n由即日起連續一星期24小時<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">狙擊狗官</span></span>，狗官所到之處要寸草不生。<br />\n<br />\n1. 咁樣做首先可以<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大大減低民意消耗</span></span>，因為所針對目標非常清晰，相信市民更容易去理解。<br />\n<br />\n2. 門檻低，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">街坊亦可以參與!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n3. 表面上似係和理非回合，但事實上班狗官有護主犬保護，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一定需要勇武去支持</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n4. 狗官長居堅離地城，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係時候要食下tg.</span></span><br />\n<br />\n5. 香港有幾大?<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">匿得去邊?</span></span>狗官大部分活動及資料都係公開。<br />\n<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢兩個月班冷氣狗官<span style=\"color: red;\">[size=5]糧就照出，依舊廢up</span></span>。 底下班黑警都叫做收錢有出汗。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">之前所有示威活動對班狗官根本係零影響!!!而家係唔係錯野唔需要付出代價!?!?</span>[/size=6]</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be09b45625b33dae5212722644fe011599096c71","tid":1430492,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T18:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e0422053bea24